    <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock screensteps-wrapper--introduction screensteps-wrapper">
  <div id="text-content_FDC69F60-743C-0137-B188-0E63FF21C970" class="text-block-content">
    <p>External apps that support LTI 1.3 and LTI Advantage require configuration using a client ID. To find the client ID, talk to your Canvas Admin.</p>
<p><strong>Note:</strong> Manually configuring an external app is an account permission. If you cannot configure an external app, this permission has not been enabled for your user role.</p>
  </div>
</div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="open_settings" data-step-uuid="FDC6B3D0-743C-0137-B189-0E63FF21C970">
    <h2 id="open_settings" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Open Settings</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/002/763/076/original/47cc9ad8-31d8-4554-a83d-9d1a8d14a3ad.png" srcset="" alt="Open Settings" height="250" width="178">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_FDC6D500-743C-0137-B18B-0E63FF21C970" class="text-block-content">
    <p>In Course Navigation, click the <strong>Settings </strong>link.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="open_apps" data-step-uuid="FDC6E780-743C-0137-B18C-0E63FF21C970">
    <h2 id="open_apps" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Open Apps</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/002/556/167/original/82729a8a-5c8d-4684-82da-e4f83202af36.png" srcset="" alt="Open Apps" height="79" width="588">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_FDC70C30-743C-0137-B18E-0E63FF21C970" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Click the <strong>Apps </strong>tab.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="view_app_configurations" data-step-uuid="FDC71F20-743C-0137-B18F-0E63FF21C970">
    <h2 id="view_app_configurations" class="step-title screensteps-heading">View App Configurations </h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/002/556/165/original/079c23d5-1a29-41c2-a1f5-271f2ce85604.png" srcset="" alt="View App Configurations " height="207" width="588">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_FDC74310-743C-0137-B191-0E63FF21C970" class="text-block-content">
    <p>To configure an app, click the <strong>View App Configurations</strong> button.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="add_new_app" data-step-uuid="FDC75450-743C-0137-B192-0E63FF21C970">
    <h2 id="add_new_app" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Add New App</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/002/556/161/original/efa5bbfe-f56e-4d4d-bb7a-1418e039e2a9.png" srcset="" alt="Add New App" height="190" width="588">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_FDC77A70-743C-0137-B194-0E63FF21C970" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Click the <strong>Add App </strong>button.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="set_configuration_type" data-step-uuid="FDC78D60-743C-0137-B195-0E63FF21C970">
    <h2 id="set_configuration_type" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Set Configuration Type</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/002/556/022/original/d583714c-1454-453a-81f0-75cb0614bac6.png" srcset="" alt="Set Configuration Type" height="169" width="768">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_FDC7B290-743C-0137-B197-0E63FF21C970" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Select the Configuration Type drop-down menu and set the configuration type to <strong>By Client ID</strong>.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="enter-client-id" data-step-uuid="FDC7C640-743C-0137-B198-0E63FF21C970">
    <h2 id="enter-client-id" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Enter Client ID</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/002/556/020/original/cd3d67eb-abaa-400b-94a7-a0ae0a794ff7.png" srcset="" alt="Enter Client ID" height="332" width="780">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_FDC7ED40-743C-0137-B19A-0E63FF21C970" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Enter the client ID in the <strong>Client ID</strong> field [1].</p>
<p>Then click the <strong>Submit</strong> button [2].</p>
<p><strong>Note: </strong>If you do not have a client ID, contact your Canvas Admin.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
        <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-2" id="view-error-message" data-step-uuid="FDC801A0-743C-0137-B19B-0E63FF21C970">
    <h3 id="view-error-message" class="step-title screensteps-heading">View Error Message</h3>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/002/556/035/original/6d506d0c-0696-427d-b196-5d99956e3df3.png" srcset="" alt="View Error Message" height="86" width="501">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_FDC82540-743C-0137-B19D-0E63FF21C970" class="text-block-content">
    <p>If the submitted client ID is not found in your account's developer keys, Canvas will display an error message.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="install-app" data-step-uuid="FDC83970-743C-0137-B19E-0E63FF21C970">
    <h2 id="install-app" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Install App</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <a href="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/002/556/016/original/e41719cf-8e89-41d6-8053-d206730336d1.png" class="screensteps-image-zoom" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">
