      </a>
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_FDC85E30-743C-0137-B1A0-0E63FF21C970" class="text-block-content">
    <p>To install the app, click the <strong>Install</strong> button.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="view-app" data-step-uuid="FDC87040-743C-0137-B1A1-0E63FF21C970">
    <h2 id="view-app" class="step-title screensteps-heading">View App</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <a href="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/002/562/093/original/a4302a60-89ab-446a-87a3-d01ca5eecdef.png" class="screensteps-image-zoom" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">
        <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/002/562/093/medium/a4302a60-89ab-446a-87a3-d01ca5eecdef.png" srcset="" alt="View App" height="566" width="855">
      </a>
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_FDC89270-743C-0137-B1A3-0E63FF21C970" class="text-block-content">
    <p>View your app [1].</p>
<p>To manage your app, click the <strong>Settings</strong> icon [2].</p>
<p>To edit the app, click the <strong>Configure </strong>link [3]. To <a href="/t5/Instructor-Guide/How-do-I-manage-external-app-placements-for-a-course/ta-p/469483" target="_blank">manage where the app displays in Canvas</a>, click the <strong>Placements </strong>link [4]. To delete the app, click the <strong>Delete </strong>link [5].</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
